00:16:12,154 --> 00:16:16,655
And if you want to speak in business terms, synergy and stocks and...

353
00:16:17,395 --> 00:16:20,357
profits and stuff, you can make lots of money on it, right?

354
00:16:20,357 --> 00:16:26,000
The strength you feel in video games makes you want to embody the heroes you see, whether

355
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:27,320
that's online or offline.

